What I wanted to see with this data was what countries have been working on increasing their overall happiness, even if they were not highly ranked. In the graph above we can see countries, like Tunisia, ranked 110th in 2023 and 70th in 2025, increase their overall happiness by over one point. Although it is easy to see which countries are doing well and ranked very happy, I believe it is important to note countries that are also improving their standards of living as well.


